*maxima-5.37.3-r2 (21 Dec 2015)

  21 Dec 2015; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> +files/50maxima-gentoo-1.el,
  +maxima-5.37.3-r2.ebuild:
  Install imaxima.

  With USE=emacs, install imaxima and byte-compile the elisp files.
  This obsoletes app-emacs/imaxima, so block against it.
  With USE=-emacs, remove any emacs files installed by the build system.

  Bug: 448242

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.26

  21 Dec 2015; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> +files/50maxima-gentoo-0.el,
  -files/50maxima-gentoo.el, maxima-5.34.1.ebuild, maxima-5.37.3-r1.ebuild:
  Rename emacs site-init file.

  Use similar naming scheme as for the patch files.

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.26

